metadata.name: KoceilaChougar.Eth
metadata.description:
Multidisciplinary artist, Mr. Koceila Chougar has long rubbed shoulders with the greatest masters of painting as well as their schools. Whether it is the descendants of Mr. Andy Warhol or the students of Mr. Salvador Dali, Mr. Koceila Chougar, in addition to being a collector knows how to give his own works the soul of the world. He also knows how to enchant with his lyrical and dreamlike sound journeys. He is one of the most interdisciplinary contemporary artists.
